{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120166_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "传令！传令！\\n斯托尔茨地区遭到魔兽袭击！\\n人员不足，紧急请求支援！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "祭司1",
            "context": "喂，又来请求支援吗？\\n负责那个地区的骑士在干什么呢？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "祭司2",
            "context": "现在哪个地区的骑士\\n都人手不足吧。\\n因为那场战争……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "祭司1",
            "context": "那场战争……\\n原来如此，是和保守派的……\\n骑士可没那么容易找到替代人选啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "祭司2",
            "context": "是啊。拒绝变革的信徒们……\\n在控制住他们之前只能忍着了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "祭司2",
            "context": "在那之前，只能靠现有的骑士\\n想办法撑住了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "祭司1",
            "context": "啊，正说着人就来了……\\n各位骑士大人也很辛苦吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "看招！\\n神圣之剑！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "嘎嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120007_01",
                "120120_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "咕噜嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "哈哈！不管你们来多少个，\\n都挡不住我们的！\\n放马过来吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "霍普，别停下脚步。\\n我们的目的不是歼灭，而是救援。\\n不断向前进就行了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "啊、对哦！\\n各位，等着我啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "斯托尔茨地区\\n居住区广场",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "到了！各位，教会骑士来救你们啦！\\n你们已经安全……诶？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "这副惨状……\\n没能赶上吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "怎、怎么会……\\n骗人、的吧？这样子……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "感伤也无济于事。\\n先搜索幸存者吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "哈！？\\n刚才，瓦砾下传来了声音！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男子",
            "context": "呜……呜呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "在这里！找到了！\\n可是这伤势……\\n得马上用治愈魔法！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "可恶……伤势太重了……\\n凭我的力量不行吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "治好……治好啊！\\n快给我治好啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男子",
            "context": "不、不用了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "不、不行！\\n现在，要是勉强自己说话……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男子",
            "context": "不用了……我已经……\\n活不久……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男子",
            "context": "不过……解脱了……\\n骑士，大人……谢……\\n呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "大叔……不、不会吧？\\n为什么……我，能救你的啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "……\\n呜、呜哇啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "来晚了吗。但不要哀叹，\\n对于逝去的生命要尽到礼数。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "无垢的灵魂啊，乘着魔力之流，\\n愿女神伊莉雅的意志与你同在……\\n安息吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "呜……呜……呜……\\n对不起……对不起啊，大叔……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "要是我能再早一些赶来……\\n我能再强一点的话……可恶！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我，要努力……变得更强。\\n强到能拯救大家……\\n呜……我要……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "变得更强……我要、努力……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "别再做白日梦了。\\n立刻给我清醒过来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "诶？师父？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "这并不是努力就能办到的事。\\n你那种想法，是幻象。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "哈、哈！？冷不丁地说啥呢！\\n我这是在给自己打气。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "毅力论吗。虽然有点道理，\\n但也不过如此。光凭你一个人的力量\\n是无法改变整个世界的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "我们不是万能的。有些地方\\n我们无法拯救，世界上的各个角落\\n不断上演着不为人知的悲剧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "也许我们能拯救一些。然而许多悲剧\\n我们甚至无法察觉，即使察觉到了\\n也很可能像这次一样来不及拯救。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "即便如此，伊莉雅的骑士\\n仍然要一边编织希望、见证死亡，\\n一边继续前进。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "你的想法与本质相去甚远。\\n拯救他人，就意味着\\n面对无法拯救的现实。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "什么！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "要想担任教会骑士，\\n就必须向残酷的世界妥协。\\n这就是为信仰而战者的义务。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "你真的\\n有面对现实的觉悟吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我、我……\\n但是……我会想办法努力！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "努力也无法改变现状。\\n即使无法改变也要奋起战斗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "为什么，要说这种话……\\n我可是，拼了命……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "因为这是事实。\\n没有觉悟的人，内心会不断\\n受到折磨。最终……消失。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "前任“天翼骑士”\\n也是如此。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "那、那个人，难道……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "他真的完美无缺——心地善良、实力强大。\\n被誉为与历代圣天骑士\\n并驾齐驱的豪杰。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "即使是那样的人，也还是消失了。\\n未能拯救的生命的那份沉重，\\n让他的内心饱受折磨……落得如此下场。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "你一开始说过……\\n不管遇到多么痛苦的事，\\n都要靠干劲和热情克服对吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "看到了这样的现实之后，\\n你还能说出这句话吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我、我……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我不知道……\\n因为……\\n努力也无能为力吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "之前我还坚信，只要努力变强\\n就能拯救全世界！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "居然还有成为“天翼骑士”\\n也无法拯救的生命……\\n我、我……根本不想知道……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我的梦想，居然那么肤浅、\\n那么渺小啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "可能是我有什么误解。\\n也许我想做的事\\n根本就没有意义……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "如果你发自内心地这么认为……\\n也许，就真的是那样吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "呜、呜呜……我已经\\n什么都搞不懂了。师父……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}